## Deprecated Agents

When agents are superseded by newer agents or decomposed into skills,
the original definitions are moved to `.github/agents/deprecated/`
rather than deleted. This preserves reference material while keeping
the active agent picker clean.

Deprecated agents are excluded from the default agent picker. They
remain available for reference or targeted invocation when needed.

The table below is maintained as agents are superseded:

| Deprecated Agent | Superseded By | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| `backlog-harvester` | `stage` + `harvest` skill | Stage absorbs triage, deliberation routing, planning, and harvest orchestration |
| `build-orchestrator` | `ship` + `build-feature` skill | Ship absorbs harness generation, build execution, review, CI, and PR lifecycle |
| `deliberator` | `stage` + `deliberate` / `spike` skills | Stage routes ideas directly to deliberate or spike skills |
| `doc-ops` | `ship` post-merge closure protocol | Ship handles knowledge graduation and doc gardening after merge |
| `memory` | Stage and Ship session continuity protocols | Session persistence is inline in both primary agents |
| `pr-review` | `ship` + `pr-lifecycle` skill | Ship manages the full PR lifecycle including review delegation |
| `review` (agent) | `review` skill | Converted from agent to skill; dispatches persona subagents |
| `plan-review` (agent) | `plan-review` skill | Converted from agent to skill; dispatches persona subagents |
| `harness-architect` (agent) | `harness-architect` skill | Converted from agent to skill; invoked by ship agent |

